Package edu.cnm.deepdive.mathmurdermystery.model.entity

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Answer
    The purpose of this entity class, Answer, is to differentiate between the answers and questions.
    Connection
    This entity will create the RoomEntity entities, with room_id for the parent columns, and for the child columns will be room_id2.
    History
    The relation between History and UserInformation will be through the user_id parents and children columns.
    Level
    This will create two different indices for scenario_id and level_title.
    MathProblem  
    RoomEntity
    This entity will keep a relation between itself and the Level class.
    Scenario
    This entity is designed to keep track of the scenario titles.
    UserInformation
    This class is used to store the user's information, progress, and score.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    MathProblem.Difficulty
    This will set the difficulty level for the problem.
    MathProblem.Type
    This sets the type of problem, whether it is boolean or multiple.
